      "value": "<div class=\"contentLayout2\"><style>[data-colorid=gcqq8yqh6v]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=gcqq8yqh6v]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=ob2hrsirdh]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=ob2hrsirdh]{color:#004eb3}[data-colorid=cv9yx58owo]{color:#4c9aff} html[data-color-mode=dark] [data-colorid=cv9yx58owo]{color:#004eb3}</style>\n<div class=\"columnLayout two-equal\" data-layout=\"two-equal\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<p><strong><span data-colorid=\"ob2hrsirdh\">Resource</span></strong>: Grunge Maps</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"cv9yx58owo\">Created by</span></strong>: <a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://www.instagram.com/eugeneriecansky/\" rel=\"nofollow\">Eugene Riecansky</a> &amp; Tom Wichitsripornkul</p><p><strong><span data-colorid=\"gcqq8yqh6v\">Use</span></strong>: Use as roughness &amp; diffuse maps</p></div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<a class=\"external-link\" href=\"https://downloads.renderman.pixar.com/RU/Textures/GrungeVol1.zip\" rel=\"nofollow\"><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-right-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-right\" alt=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" width=\"200\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/609157121/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356145241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/609157121/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356145241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"68\" data-width=\"286\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"609157143\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"attachment\" data-linked-resource-default-alias=\"b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png\" data-base-url=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki\" data-linked-resource-content-type=\"image/png\" data-linked-resource-container-id=\"609157121\" data-linked-resource-container-version=\"5\" data-media-id=\"2dddb583-54be-493a-9469-243680d3bd12\" data-media-type=\"file\" srcset=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/609157121/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356145241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=286&amp;height=68 2x, https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/609157121/b764f225-9112-4313-ba5a-1f74750b8767.png?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356145241&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=200&amp;height=47 1x\" /></span></a><p /></div>\n</div>\n</div>\n<div class=\"columnLayout fixed-width\" data-layout=\"fixed-width\">\n<div class=\"cell normal\" data-type=\"normal\">\n<div class=\"innerCell\">\n<hr /><h1 id=\"GrungeMapsVol.1-Overview\">Overview</h1><p>A collection of grunge, smudge, and edge breakup maps for you to use in your projects.<br />Add to your diffuse network to add variation, roughness map or anisotropy networks</p><span class=\"confluence-embedded-file-wrapper image-center-wrapper confluence-embedded-manual-size\"><img class=\"confluence-embedded-image image-center\" alt=\"GrungeMaps_preview.jpg\" width=\"760\" loading=\"lazy\" src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/thumbnails/609157121/GrungeMaps_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356516082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2&amp;width=760&amp;height=768\" data-image-src=\"https://renderman.atlassian.net/wiki/download/attachments/609157121/GrungeMaps_preview.jpg?version=1&amp;modificationDate=1758356516082&amp;cacheVersion=1&amp;api=v2\" data-height=\"1677\" data-width=\"1658\" data-unresolved-comment-count=\"0\" data-linked-resource-id=\"608665790\" data-linked-resource-version=\"1\" data-linked-resource-type=\"